{
  "stem": "182.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you remember what happened in the first-- after the First World War, that you were left without nothing because you did bad things.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, I don't know whether they understood or whether this meant anything to them, but they took us to a big-- I don't know if you could call it a farm, but it was a place where they had racehorses.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Not now, but before.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was a big, big barn with beautiful porcelain bowls for the horses to eat from and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they housed us there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was an attic, and there was a lower part.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the 500 people were there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, there was a well where we could take water and wash ourselves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The food-- we had a kettle where we boiled some potato and carrots, or I don't know what.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Some little thing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it is very, very poor, very nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were there also, oh, about 10 days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father went into the village to get some kind of medication because we had nothing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was the only physician in the whole group.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they gave it to him, and they were very nice to him in the village.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And also he could talk to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a doctor who spoke fluently Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was not a Jew, but he spoke fluently Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he told my father that, you know, doctor-- we are so short of doctors here-- there was a typhoid epidemic-- that I would like you to stay here.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, first my father said that, you know, I'm the only physician with the group, and I feel that I have to go with them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he says, no, no, you talk it over with your wife, and you stay here.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
